<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَلاسْتِيفَائِهِ ثَلَاثَةُ شُرُوطٍ <span class="c2">(١)</span>:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> تَكْلِيفُ مُسْتَحِقٍّ لَهُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَاتِّفَاقُهُمْ عَلَيْهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> وَأَنْ يُؤْمَنَ فِي اسْتِيفَائِهِ تَعَدِّيهِ إِلَى غَيْرِ جَانٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَيُحْبَسُ لِقُدُومِ غَائِبٍ، وَبُلُوغٍ، وَإِفَاقَةٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيَجِبُ اسْتِيفَاؤُهُ:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- بِحَضْرَةِ سُلْطَانٍ أَوْ نَائِبِهِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- وَبِآلَةٍ مَاضِيَةٍ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَفِي النَّفْسِ:</span> بِضَرْبِ العُنُقِ بِسَيْفٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيَجِبُ بِعَمْدٍ:</span> القَوَدُ أَوِ الدِّيَةُ، فَيُخَيَّرُ وَلِيٌّ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- وَالعَفْوُ مَجَّاناً أَفْضَلُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَمَتَى:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- اخْتَارَ الدِّيَةَ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) قوله: (شروط) سقطت من (أ) و (ج) و (د).<br>(٢) في (ج): ويجب استيفاؤه بآلة ماضية بحضرة سلطان أو نائبه.</p> </div>